<!-- Donors Help -->
<div class="help-section">
    <nav class="help-breadcrumb"><a href="/help">Help</a> / <span>Donors</span></nav>
    <h1><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> Donors</h1>
    <p class="help-intro">Track and manage your supporters.</p>
    
    <div class="help-block">
        <h2>Why Track Donors?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Generate year-end tax receipts</li>
            <li>Track giving history and patterns</li>
            <li>Identify major donors and prospects</li>
            <li>Measure donor retention</li>
            <li>Personalize thank-you communications</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="help-block">
        <h2>Donor Types</h2>
        <table class="help-table">
            <tr><td><strong>Individual</strong></td><td>Personal donations from people</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Business</strong></td><td>Corporate donations, sponsorships</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Foundation</strong></td><td>Private foundations, community foundations</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Government</strong></td><td>Government agencies (usually grants)</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Organization</strong></td><td>Civic groups, other nonprofits</td></tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    
    <div class="help-block">
        <h2>Donor Fields</h2>
        <table class="help-table field-table">
            <tr><td><strong>Name</strong></td><td>Full name or organization name</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Type</strong></td><td>Individual, Business, Foundation, etc.</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Email</strong></td><td>For sending tax receipts electronically</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Phone</strong></td><td>Contact phone number</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Address</strong></td><td>Mailing address for receipts</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Anonymous</strong></td><td>If checked, name hidden on public lists</td></tr>
            <tr><td><strong>Notes</strong></td><td>Internal notes about the donor</td></tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    
    <div class="help-block">
        <h2>Automatic Tracking</h2>
        <p>When you link donations to donors, the system automatically tracks:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Total Contributions</strong> - Lifetime giving amount</li>
            <li><strong>First Contribution</strong> - Date of first gift</li>
            <li><strong>Last Contribution</strong> - Most recent gift date</li>
            <li><strong>Giving History</strong> - All linked transactions</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="help-tip">
        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
        <strong>Tip:</strong> Always link income transactions to donors! This enables automatic tax receipt generation.
    </div>
</div>
